parameters: You were also eaten by the Wolf.
I was tricked by Mr. Wolf and with his p…penis...
Treating my sweet granddaughter so horribly…
I would fill his stomach up with a mountain of stones,
And give him a taste of hell!!
"Oh there, there…it was scary, wasn't it?
If only I could hold you in my arms…
After being eaten by the Wolf,
I tried to escape from here but…
"I got caught by a monster that melts
And was turned into this form.
So, that means….Grandma is…cry…no it can't be…
This is no time to feel sad.
"You must escape from here as soon as possible.
"We are inside the body of the Wolf.
Normally, once eaten by a Wolf
Mr. Wolf's body is much bigger than ours but
it is strange that the inside of his body is this wide inside…
"It seems the Wolf hasn't realized this himself yet.
A normal wolf doesn't usually walk on two legs
"He must be a living creature transformed
I have no doubt about this.
"I thought this was strange as well.
Mr. Wolf is not a normal wolf?
"Yes, I am quite sure of this.
"I was surprised when I arrived here after getting eaten.
Desperate to escape, I was going back and forth,
only to find the "unusual place with magic".
"It seems as though you can escape from here.
But, the monster that melted me
"If you successfully run away from it
I am nothing but a heap of bones now.
"I want at least…such a sweet girl like you to survive.
So, please try your best and go on, Blanchette!
I, I'll do my best to find the exit!
I have one more piece of advice to help you get out.
"The inside of this body is not only intricate,
but there are creepy tentacles all over the place
sure to try blocking your path.
"Here and there inside of this body, you can find
something like "shards of metal" that you can use
to cut open these obstacles and move on ahead.
"I, I'm going to survive and return home…!
\C[10]Try to destroy Blanchette's sense of hope.
You were cut to pieces by a cornered Blanchette…
at least 3 sharp shards in her possession,
Do you want to try again?
